This script is a Chocobo digging addon to be used with Windower for Final
Fantasy XI.

You can report issues, get the latest version, and view the source at:
  http://github.com/svanheulen/digger-windower-addon

To install this addon, create a folder called "digger" inside the Windower
addons folder (most likely C:\Program Files (x86)\Windower4\addons) and copy
the digger.lua file there.

To run this addon, in the Final Fantasy XI input line type:
//lua load digger

After the addon is loaded you can set you digging rank by typing:
//digger rank <rank>

Just replace <rank> with amateur, recruit, initiate, etc.

You can also reset the dig accuracy statistics by typing:
//digger reset
